'''2016年朱巴军事冲突'''指[[苏丹人民解放军|苏丹人民解放军]]分别效忠于总统[[萨尔瓦·基尔·马亚尔迪特|萨尔瓦·基尔·马亚尔迪特]]和副总统[[里克·马查尔|里克·马查尔]]的敌对派系之间的一系列冲突<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|date=2016-07-11|access-date=2016-07-11|url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/world-news/civil-war-fears-as-as-heavy-arms-fire-rocks-south-sudan-capital-34872636.html?|agency=Associated Press|title=Civil war fears as as heavy arms fire rocks South Sudan capital,}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
2015年8月，双方曾签署停火协议，尝试结束南苏丹内战。后来[[里克·马查尔|里克·马查尔]]于2016年4月出任副总统<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36140423|title=South Sudan rebel chief Riek Machar sworn in as vice-president|date=2016-04-26|access-date=2016-07-11|publisher=BBC|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704230446/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36140423|archive-date=2016-07-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 过程 ==
7月7日，亲基尔派士兵截停车辆，搜查是否有马查尔支持者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-south-sudan-security-casualties-idUSKCN0ZQ08J|title=Renewed fighting erupts in South Sudan as fears of civil war mount|first=Denis|last=Dumo|first2=Michelle|last2=Nichols|date=2016-07-10|accessdate=2016-07-11|publisher=Reuters|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710231524/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-south-sudan-security-casualties-idUSKCN0ZQ08J|archive-date=2016-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之后支持马查尔的士兵开火袭击一处政府检查站<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36744636|title=South Sudan: Heavy gunfire following death of soldiers|publisher=BBC|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708231859/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36744636|archive-date=2016-07-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事件导致五名政府军士兵死亡，两名未认定所属派系的士兵受伤<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2016-07-10|publisher=Xinhua|date=2016-07-08|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-07/09/c_135499508.htm|title=South Sudan leaders appeal for calm after clashes in Juba|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709145039/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-07/09/c_135499508.htm|archive-date=2016-07-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/11/world/africa/south-sudan-fighting.html|title=New Wave of Violence Ripples Through South Sudan’s Capital|last=Fortin|first=Jacey|date=2016-07-10|last2=Kron|first2=Josh|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710221455/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/11/world/africa/south-sudan-fighting.html|archive-date=2016-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

8日，总统基尔和副总统马查尔进行和平谈判的政府大楼附近爆发战斗<ref name="poiuyt">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-southsudan-security-idUSKCN0ZP075|title=At least 115 soldiers killed in South Sudan clashes: opposition|date=2016-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-09|publisher=Reuters|last=Dumo|first=Denis|last2=Biryabarema|first2=Elias|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710021858/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-southsudan-security-idUSKCN0ZP075|archive-date=2016-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最初参与的势力是基尔和马查尔的保镖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/international/2016-07-10/at-least-150-soldiers-killed-as-south-sudan-marks-fifth-independence-anniversary/1597512?|publisher=ABC|title=At least 150 soldiers killed as South Sudan marks fifth independence anniversary|date=2016-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710151948/http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/international/2016-07-10/at-least-150-soldiers-killed-as-south-sudan-marks-fifth-independence-anniversary/1597512|archive-date=2016-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。军营附近也发生冲突。一处联合国基地外面发生枪击事件<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Al Jazeera|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/07/south-sudan-scores-dead-independence-anniversary-160709090438275.html|title=South Sudan: 'Scores dead' on independence anniversary|date=2016-07-09|access-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709120251/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/07/south-sudan-scores-dead-independence-anniversary-160709090438275.html|archive-date=2016-07-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，据报一人死亡<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Gulf Today|url=http://gulftoday.ae/portal/86bfdc4d-b832-49bb-826f-0f7c149a40bd.aspx?|title=S.Sudan clashes kill over 150 soldiers|date=2016-07-09|access-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709211409/http://gulftoday.ae/portal/86bfdc4d-b832-49bb-826f-0f7c149a40bd.aspx|archive-date=2016-07-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。冲突过后，重兵驻守朱巴<ref name="poiuyt"/>。当日的战斗造成35名反对派士兵和80名政府军士兵死亡<ref name="poiuyt"/>。

10日，相对平静的一天过后，朱巴再次爆发战斗。战斗主要集中在叛军基地所在地杰贝尔和古德乐附近<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/world/renewed-fighting-breaks-out-across-south-sudan-capital-1.2980833|title=Renewed fighting breaks out across South Sudan capital|date=2016-07-10|publisher=CTV|access-date=2016-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912101632/https://www.ctvnews.ca/world/heavy-arms-fire-rocks-south-sudan-capital-many-casualties-1.2980833|archive-date=2019-09-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。机场附近传出爆炸声和枪声<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/07/south-sudan-fighting-gunfire-erupts-juba-160710064423699.html|title=South Sudan fighting: Gunfire erupts again in Juba|date=2016-07-10|access-date=2016-07-10|publisher=Al Jazeera|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710081655/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/07/south-sudan-fighting-gunfire-erupts-juba-160710064423699.html|archive-date=2016-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名[[联合国维和部队|联合国维和人员]]身亡，两人负重伤<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Reuters|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-south-sudan-security-casualties-idUSKCN0ZQ08J|title=Renewed fighting erupts in South Sudan as fears of civil war mount|last=Dumo|first=Denis|date=2016-07-10|access-date=2016-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710092458/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-south-sudan-security-casualties-idUSKCN0ZQ08J|archive-date=2016-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。政府军轰炸了杰贝尔的叛军营地。战斗在雷爆开始时结束<ref name="a"/>。包括33名平民在内的272人在当日的战斗中遇害<ref>{{cite web|title=Up to 272 dead in South Sudan, mortars & RPGs fired near UN compound|url=https://www.rt.com/news/350438-south-sudan-fighting-un/|website=rt.com|publisher=Russia Today|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711114357/https://www.rt.com/news/350438-south-sudan-fighting-un/|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

11日，朱巴继续打仗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36762831|title=South Sudan: Clashes erupt in Juba hours after UN plea|publisher=BBC|date=2016-07-11|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711222702/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36762831|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。古德尔和杰贝尔仍然是暴力事件的热点。爆炸袭击中了机场、使馆区和联合国基地所在地唐普宁<ref>{{cite web|publisher=France 24|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20160711-south-sudan-very-heavy-fighting-juba-kiir-machar?|title=Explosions and heavy weapons gunfire shook South Sudan's capital, Juba, Monday in the fifth day of clashes between government and opposition forces, raising the spectre of a return to civil war.|date=2016-07-11|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711200539/http://www.france24.com/en/20160711-south-sudan-very-heavy-fighting-juba-kiir-machar|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在闹市区可听见迫击炮声<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/07/south-sudan-security-council-demands-ceasefire-160711043656662.html|title=South Sudan crisis: Renewed fighting in Juba|date=2015-07-11|publisher=Al Jazeera|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711080625/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/07/south-sudan-security-council-demands-ceasefire-160711043656662.html|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。联合国证实7月10日有两名中国维和人员被打死<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-07/11/c_135505093.htm?|title=Two Chinese UN peacekeepers killed in South Sudan capital fighting|publisher=新华社|date=2016-07-11|access-date=20016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712130618/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-07/11/c_135505093.htm|archive-date=2016-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另有8名受伤。8人在联合国难民营被打死，59人在炮火中受伤<ref>{{cite web|publisher=CBC|date=2016-07-11|access-date=2016-07-11|last=Thompson|first=Carolyn|title='A tent cannot stop a bullet': 8 killed and dozens injured at UN camp in South Sudan|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/south-sudan-violence-jaba-ceasefire-1.3674019?cmp=rss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160714203531/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/south-sudan-violence-jaba-ceasefire-1.3674019?cmp=rss|archive-date=2016-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。虽然宣布停火<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/07/south-sudan-president-declares-unilateral-ceasefire-160711151349444.html|access-date=2016-07-12|date=2016-07-11|publisher=Al Jazeera|title=South Sudan's warring factions declare ceasefire|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711182907/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/07/south-sudan-president-declares-unilateral-ceasefire-160711151349444.html|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但枪声的报告仍然持续<ref name="z">{{cite web|publisher=BBC|title=South Sudan clashes: Salva Kiir and Riek Machar order ceasefire|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36763076|date=2016-07-11|access-date=2016-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160713062245/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36763076|archive-date=2016-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 各方反应 ==
基尔和马查尔均谴责冲突<ref name="poiuyt"/>。

{{flag|UN}}：[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]表示：“我对目前在朱巴发生激烈战斗感到震惊和惊骇。我强烈呼吁基尔总统和第一副总统里克·马查尔在他们的权力范围内尽一切能力立即缓和敌对行动，下令他们各自的军队脱离接触，撤回到他们的基地。这种毫无意义的暴力行为是不可接受的，有可能会扭转目前在和平进程中取得的进展......<ref name="a">{{cite web|publisher=Japan Times|date=2016-07-11|access-date=2016-07-11|url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2016/07/11/world/south-sudan-fears-return-civil-war-heavy-fighting-erupts-anew-juba-thousands-flee/?#.V4Lh07srK01|title=South Sudan fears return to civil war as heavy fighting erupts anew in Juba, thousands flee|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160714202741/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2016/07/11/world/south-sudan-fears-return-civil-war-heavy-fighting-erupts-anew-juba-thousands-flee#.V4Lh07srK01|archive-date=2016-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/sg/statements/index.asp?nid=9872|title=Statement by the Secretary-General on South Sudan|date=2016-07-10|access-date=2016-07-11|publisher=UN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711114332/http://www.un.org/sg/statements/index.asp?nid=9872|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>”[[联合国安理会|联合国安理会]]在针对危机的紧急会议后，发出声明呼吁立刻停止战斗、基尔和马沙尔尽最大努力管控他们各自的军队<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=54426#.V4MMgriGOUk|title=Security Council condemns fighting in Juba, demands South Sudan's leaders prevent spread of violence|publisher=UN News Centre|date=2016-07-10|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711114251/http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=54426#.V4MMgriGOUk|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|联合国驻南苏丹特派团|United Nations Mission in South Sudan}}已经在其营地增派巡逻人手<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/10/south-sudan-capital-juba-violence-salva-kiir|title=More than 300 dead as South Sudan capital is rocked by violence|last=Burke|first=Jason|date=2016-07-11|website=the Guardian|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710214211/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/10/south-sudan-capital-juba-violence-salva-kiir|archive-date=2016-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{flag|Sudan}}：苏丹总统[[奥马尔·巴希尔|奥马尔·巴希尔]]在电话中敦促基尔和马查尔自我控制<ref>{{cite web|publisher=新华社|title=Khartoum expresses deep concern over conflicts in S. Sudan|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-07/11/c_135502590.htm?|date=2016-07-10|access-date=2016-07-11|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711121149/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-07/11/c_135502590.htm|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{flag|USA}}：谴责暴力事件，呼吁各方立即制止他们的军队继续战斗，撤回他们的营地，防止出现更多的暴力行为和流血事件<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.itv.com/news/update/2016-07-11/us-demands-an-immediate-end-to-south-sudan-violence/?|title=US demands an immediate end to South Sudan violence|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712131722/http://www.itv.com/news/update/2016-07-11/us-demands-an-immediate-end-to-south-sudan-violence/|archive-date=2016-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2016/07/259511.htm?|title=South Sudan: United States Demands an Immediate End to Fighting in South Sudan|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712042106/http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2016/07/259511.htm|archive-date=2016-07-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

{{flag|CHN}}：[[中华人民共和国外交部|外交部]][[陆慷|陆慷]]在例行记者会上谴责了袭击事件，并向牺牲人员表示深切哀悼，对受伤人员和伤亡人员家属表示诚挚慰问。他要求南苏丹政府彻查此起事件，严惩肇事者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1379147.shtml|title=2016年7月11日外交部发言人陆慷主持例行记者会|website=中华人民共和国外交部网站|date=2016-07-11|access-date=2016-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712122518/http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1379147.shtml|archive-date=2016-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

